            <title>[HBASE-2229] convert all command line parsing to jopt simple</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-2229</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;what we are doing right now is wonky, we should use jopt simple, which attempts to emulate ye olde classic opt parsers from C in their brevity and terseness.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://jopt-simple.sourceforge.net/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;http://jopt-simple.sourceforge.net/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
